        <heading>1313.  Partition suits by emancipated minors</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1313.  Partition suits by emancipated minors.
Minors who are emancipated to enable them to administer their estate can, with the same authorization and with the assistance of their curators ad lites , sue for the partition of property in which they are interested.</p>
        </content>
